  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to see scroll bar to navigate through chat history easily.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n*Summary*: the scroll bar is missing in public and 1-1 chats\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nscroll bar is presented, so I can pull it and easily navigate through chat history\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nno scroll bar is presented.\r\nNOTE: on both IOS and Android mobile apps scroll bar is presented.\r\n<img width=\"568\" alt=\"noscr\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/43950408-e1e7b6b0-9c98-11e8-97cc-b4b8afe39440.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Join any public chat with long history (need to scroll to see all messages)\r\n- Scroll to the top to see previous messages\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: nightly 10/08/2018\r\n* Operating System: Mac OS x High Sierra\r\n",
